              Eligibility for participating in Orientation Programme 
            </a>
          </h4>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseThree" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingThree">
          <div class="panel-body">
              Orientation is for the newly appointed teachers. 
          </div>
          <!-- Panel body -->
        </div>
